title: Touch for Health, Book 1 - Toni Lilley.pdf
description:
This manual was written for Touch for Health students to enable them to learn the kinesiology techniques that
allow them to work with themselves, their friends and family. It is not designed to teach people how to treat,
diagnose or prescribe. The responsibility always lies with the person who chooses muscle testing as a tool to
gauge energetic responses to foods, supplements and substances, and to act upon this knowledge as he or she
chooses
